<div id="main_content">
	<h2>Art in Motion: SunRail-Inspired Exhibit Features UCF Installation</h2>
	
	<p class="article_info">
		
			By Courtney Gilmartin
		
		<span class="date">Aug. 13, 2010</span></p>
	
	
	
		<div class="article_img" style="width: 345px;">

			<img alt="Article Main Picture" src="../resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/2000/NE2226/en_US/whatmovesyoumain.jpg" height="226" width="345"  /> 
			
			<p>Viewers of the installation are asked to respond to the question, "What moves you?" Their answers are projected onto the sphere.</p>
			
				<p class="note"><a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=0024004107a42ec8a01289848d7ab02931">Full Photo</a></p>
			
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
		</div>
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
		
